    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is priced to reflect its history as a dependable daily driver. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including several visible scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows wear and some staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads or a suspension tune-up. It is a solid, functional choice for a buyer looking for a reliable vehicle at an affordable price point without expecting aesthetic perfection.",
