    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire an automotive masterpiece in showroom-original condition. This vehicle has been curated with uncompromising attention to detail, maintaining a level of preservation that must be seen to be fully appreciated. Every surface reflects its factory-fresh heritage, from the flawless finish to the pristine, meticulously maintained interior. Mechanically superior and cosmetically impeccable, this example represents the definitive standard for its class. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than excellence, this is an investment in quality that stands above the rest.",
      "price": 48900.0,
