    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this absolute beauty go. This isn't just a car to me; it\u2019s been my pride and joy, always garage-kept and pampered like a member of the family. It is in truly stunning shape\u2014inside and out, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every time I get behind the wheel, it brings a massive smile to my face, and I know it\u2019ll do the same for you. It\u2019s ready for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come on by, let's talk shop, and I\u2019ll show you why this gem is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 44900.0,
